children.tooltip: Make sure that you remember your credentials!

children.text:
Please pay attention!
These credentials will only be displayed once, you need to remember them before signing in.

Please ensure that we receive this order response structure from your end:

{ "items": [ { "id": 1, "name": "your product name", "price": 1600, "quantity": 4 } ], "payment_method": "cash" (or "card") } ]}
